snippet.title: Candleholder - UNDEREVENT 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more about the project here!
https://huecycles.com/candleholder

Join our Discord Server!
https://discord.gg/3TsSY5m7ns

Trailer edited by @LVoidtheEndless 
Animation by HUECYCLES & Nebytou
https://twitter.com/Nebytou

Animation Help by @marineflames and @Lisspeed 

Full trailer music, done by rata/grosezero
https://soundcloud.com/huecycles/bsotw-trailer

Dealmaker Voice Acting by TC
https://loathemetc.tumblr.com/

Watch UNDEREVENT 2023 here!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ansCGZUhtVk

Candleholder is a Deltarune fangame in early development.
Thank you for tuning in!
